meta:
    title: "FlowFuse Cloud"
    description: "Fully hosted service to build, manage, and deploy Node-RED applications without the hassle of setting up your own cloud infrastructure"
    keywords: 
    faq:
        - question: "How much does FlowFuse Cloud cost?"
          answer: >
            After the 2-week free trial, the Starter Tier costs $20 a month for 2 team members, 2 hosted Node-RED instances and 2 remote Node-RED instances. For more details on advanced tiers and features see <a href='/pricing/'>Pricing</a>.
        - question: "Does FlowFuse offer annual discounts for FlowFuse Cloud?"    
          answer: >
            Yes, we offer a 10% discount for annual subscriptions. Please <a href='/contact-us/'>reach out</a> to request the discount.
        - question: "Do I need a Credit Card to get started?"    
          answer: >
            No, you don’t need a credit card to sign up for the 14-day free trial.
        - question: "What features are included in FlowFuse Cloud vs Self-hosted?"
          answer: >
            At the Enterprise level, all features are available both on the Cloud and Self hosted deployment. For more details on the tiers and available features see <a href='/pricing/'>Pricing</a>. 
